[FILE:434:descriptions/desc.primary]
fheroes2 is a recreation of the Heroes of Might and Magic II game engine.

This open source multiplatform project, written from scratch, is designed 
to reproduce the original game with significant improvements in gameplay, 
graphics and logic (including support for high-resolution graphics, 
improved AI, numerous fixes and user interface improvements), breathing 
new life into one of the most addictive turn-based strategy games.


